  "prompt": "What are some shows like Ellen and Dr. Phil?",
  "response": "If you enjoy shows like \"The Ellen DeGeneres Show\" and \"Dr. Phil,\" here are some other daytime talk shows and reality-based programs that might appeal to you:\n\n1. **The Kelly Clarkson Show** - Featuring Kelly Clarkson, this show combines celebrity interviews, musical performances, and feel-good stories.\n\n2. **The Drew Barrymore Show** - Drew Barrymore hosts a mix of celebrity interviews, emotional stories, and entertaining segments.\n\n3. **Maury** - Known for its dramatic paternity tests and relationship dilemmas, this show dives into personal stories and conflicts.\n\n4. **The Talk** - A panel of women discusses current issues and shares personal experiences, along with celebrity guests and news highlights.\n\n5. **The Dr. Oz Show** - Focused on health and wellness, Dr. Oz addresses medical topics, offers health advice, and features inspiring guests.\n\n6. **Live with Kelly and Mark** - A daytime talk show featuring interviews with celebrities and discussions on various topics, hosted by Kelly Ripa and Mark Consuelos.\n\n7. **Rachel Ray Show** - Combining cooking and lifestyle segments, Rachael Ray invites guests to share recipes and stories while offering practical tips.\n\n8. **Tamron Hall** - A blend of news, celebrity interviews, and personal stories from everyday people, hosted by journalist Tamron Hall.\n\n9. **Steve Wilkos Show** - A talk show dealing with serious social issues and conflicts, hosted by former \"Jerry Springer\" security guard Steve Wilkos.\n\n10. **The View** - A panel of women discusses current events, politics, and culture, often featuring celebrity interviews and guest hosts.\n\nThese shows typically feature interviews, personal stories, and discussions around relatable topics, making them similar in tone and format to \"Ellen\" and \"Dr. Phil.\"",
